divs: Sighting DetailsWent out to rear garden to lock up shed, looked up and saw 4 craft flying in triangle formation with a fourth at the rear. Took about 3 seconds to fly from West to East. At 2 seconds they seemed to join together and shoot off to the horizon. No sound or trails left behind.
